name: Amy X
description: I’m a honest, open and loving woman who is settled and happy with my life. I believe in good communication, strong affection, loyalty and kindness. I like fun and can find it doing most anything. I’ve been told I have a good sensand of humor….I enjoy lots of affection and believe it’s part of the glue that keeps a relationship together. Of course that along with good communication, mutual respect and obviously sharing some tastes for the same things. I love to travel and I love to kiss. A man with wrinkles from laughing too much, emotionally available, extremely funny and very smart. A co conspirator who craves the outdoors. A strong independent man who wants a woman in kind. Knows there is great beauty in quiet, with a time and place for the music of life. Looks in the mirror and likes what he sees.
